## 3) Canonical product and market buckets

Use these buckets when classifying GearGrid content:

1. Fire & EMS storage
2. Athletic & Education storage
3. Public Works storage
4. Tactical storage
5. Locker systems
6. Shelving, benches, racks, and accessories
7. Facility storage planning

